    ape,
    collapse,
    data.table,
    parallel,
    parallelDist,
    Rcpp,
    RcppParallel,
    RcppXPtrUtils,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    RcppParallel
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
